# The `SwappedData` Struct Reference

<DoxygenPage pluginConfig={pluginConfig}>

When the GSYM file&#39;s endianness doesn&#39;t match the host system then we must decode all data structures that need to be swapped into local storage and set point the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/arrayref">ArrayRef</a> objects above to these swapped copies. <a href="#details">More...</a>

## Description {#details}

When the GSYM file&#39;s endianness doesn&#39;t match the host system then we must decode all data structures that need to be swapped into local storage and set point the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/arrayref">ArrayRef</a> objects above to these swapped copies.
